reviewText: Splendid Western.  Sterling Hayden is his usual tough self and Yvonne De Carlo is as voluptuous as ever.  Gritty and downright enjoyable.

normal  ''b'' grade western,
was disappointed, expected a better movie,
maybe I have my hopes far too high.

After reading the editorial review on this movie & seeing some of the film shorts i decided to purchase
this western it was well worth it i am sure you will enjoy it as well.
